{"tid":1535302,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[真心]各位讀書連登仔請入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:48:34.000Z","uid":176313,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7122dd14dbc824947f0b0e9b7a80cef78c3dd7","tid":1535302,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"宜家抗爭已經係進入一個長期嘅階段，大家除咗努力出街爭取，除咗罷課罷買，仲要做一樣好重要嘅嘢，就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要讀好書！</span></span></strong><br />\n你哋係香港嘅未來，所以一定要做香港嘅棟梁，只有讀好書，你哋先可以喺日後，為香港做到更多嘢！如果你哋以前對讀書仲係一種玩玩下嘅態度，希望你哋跟住落嚟，就算唔翻學，都要將書讀好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為香港未來！罷課不罷學！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"deec53d5dc80e8c6870fc9c9160724cd6a1c9f45","tid":1535302,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3cd8fc2e82950a095290d0444a7304dae4f20ba","tid":1535302,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c6aa57df65a8f15e887991da3e89d6499a47827","tid":1535302,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"推！各自努力！"},{"pid":"f11d23e17f5b27449ab77d62e884e4d4c53467f8","tid":1535302,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"02b7cd2ab2f7c5a363a35c7a5c4374f4acf038fc","tid":1535302,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"就算日後俾狗拉，都唔好放棄學業！為香港！"},{"pid":"035072dec89a23e0e1d9e8e42912ea2b4ffc2a49","tid":1535302,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"記得，為香港，既要抗爭，亦要讀書！"},{"pid":"e461174a14bd2f7aed76aa323439da39544e8862","tid":1535302,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"推！好好讀書！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08a7bfe85393415